nce\n\n    Step into a fully immersive VR world where every slash of your katana and every shot from your gun feels real. The high-fidelity graphics and realistic soundscapes create an unparalleled sense of presence and engagement.", "short_description": "Storyline\n\nIn a world torn apart by war and chaos, the ancient art of the ninja is the last hope for survival. As the world descends into darkness, you, a skilled ninja warrior, must defend against relentless assaults using your katana and futuristic gun. Set against the backdrop of a war-torn landscape illuminated by the dying light of the setting sun, \"Ninja's Last Stand\" immerses you in a gripping narrative of honor, duty, and survival."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/ninjas-last-stand/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "WHR26 Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/ninjas-last-stand", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7691412447623754"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1012213793746802"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1012213793746802"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_time": 1721704590, "status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1012213793746802"}]}, "li